#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:9
msgid "tmux導入メモ"
msgstr "tmux introduction memo"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:11
msgid ""
"linux環境でセッションが切れても再開できる仕掛けであるtmuxについて導入し利用していきます。インストールと最小限の操作方法をまとめました。"
msgstr ""
"We will introduce and use tmux, which is a mechanism that allows you to "
"restart a session even if it expires in a Linux environment. We have "
"summarized the installation and minimal operation method."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:18
msgid "インストール"
msgstr "install"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:25
msgid "バージョン確認："
msgstr "Check version:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:31
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:66
#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:90
msgid "---"
msgstr "---"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:34
msgid "最低限おさえておきたい操作"
msgstr "Operations you should keep at a minimum"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:37
msgid "セッション操作"
msgstr "Session operations"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:39
msgid "新規セッション作成: ``tmux``"
msgstr "Create a new session: ``tmux``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:40
msgid "新規セッション作成(名前付き): ``tmux new -s mysession``"
msgstr "Create a new session (with name): ``tmux new -s mysession``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:41
msgid "セッション一覧: ``tmux ls``"
msgstr "Session list: ``tmux ls``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:42
msgid "セッションへ接続: ``tmux attach -t mysession``"
msgstr "Connect to a session: ``tmux attach -t mysession``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:43
msgid "セッションへ接続(簡易版): ``tmux a``"
msgstr "Connect to session (simple version): ``tmux a``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:44
msgid "セッション離脱（デタッチ）: ``Ctrl-b d``"
msgstr "Detach session: ``Ctrl-b d``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:45
msgid "セッション終了: セッション内で ``exit`` または ``Ctrl-d``"
msgstr "Exiting a session: ``exit`` or ``Ctrl-d`` within a session"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:46
msgid "tmuxの再起動: ``tmux kill-server``"
msgstr "Restart tmux: ``tmux kill-server``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:49
msgid "ウィンドウ操作"
msgstr "Window operation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:51
msgid "新規ウィンドウ作成: ``Ctrl-b c``"
msgstr "Create a new window: ``Ctrl-b c``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:52
msgid "ウィンドウ切り替え: ``Ctrl-b n`` （次） / ``Ctrl-b p`` （前）"
msgstr "Switch windows: ``Ctrl-b n`` (next) / ``Ctrl-b p`` (previous)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:53
msgid "ウィンドウ名変更: ``Ctrl-b ,``"
msgstr "Rename window: ``Ctrl-b ,``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:56
msgid "ペイン操作"
msgstr "Pane operations"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:57
msgid "ペイン分割: ``Ctrl-b %`` （縦） / ``Ctrl-b \"`` （横）"
msgstr "Pane split: ``Ctrl-b %`` (vertical) / ``Ctrl-b \"`` (horizontal)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:58
msgid "ペインの切り替え: ``Ctrl-b o`` （次のペイン） / ``Ctrl-b ;`` （前のペイン）"
msgstr "Switch panes: ``Ctrl-b o`` (next pane) / ``Ctrl-b ;`` (previous pane)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:59
msgid "ペインの切り替え: ``Ctrl-b`` + 矢印キー"
msgstr "Switch panes: ``Ctrl-b`` + arrow keys"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:60
msgid "ペイン最大化: ``Ctrl-b z`` （再度押すと元に戻る）"
msgstr "Maximize pane: ``Ctrl-b z`` (press again to restore)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:61
msgid "ペインのサイズ調整: ``Ctrl-b`` → ``:`` , ``resize-pane -D/U/L/R``"
msgstr "Resize pane: ``Ctrl-b`` → ``:`` , ``resize-pane -D/U/L/R``"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:64
msgid "ペイン分割のデフォルトキー割り当ては分かりにくい。キー変更は.tmux.conf設定を参照。"
msgstr ""
"The default key assignments for pane splitting are confusing. For key "
"changes, refer to .tmux.conf settings."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:69
msgid ".tmux.conf の最低限設定"
msgstr "Minimum .tmux.conf settings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:71
msgid "`\"` や `%` によるペイン分割操作を、より直感的な記号に置き換えた設定です。 また、デフォルトの分割キーは無効化しています。"
msgstr ""
"This setting replaces pane splitting operations using `\"` and `%` with more"
" intuitive symbols. Also, the default splitting key is disabled."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:74
msgid "以下を ``~/.tmux.conf`` に記載："
msgstr "Add the following to ``~/.tmux.conf``:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:83
msgid "この設定により、以下の操作が可能になります："
msgstr "This setting allows you to:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:85
msgid "``Ctrl-b \\\\`` : 横（左右）に分割"
msgstr "``Ctrl-b \\\\``: Split horizontally (left and right)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:86
msgid "``Ctrl-b -`` : 縦（上下）に分割"
msgstr "``Ctrl-b -`` : Split vertically (up and down)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-10-tmux-setup.rst:88
msgid "記号の形状から、分割方向が直感的にわかるようになります。"
msgstr ""
"You can intuitively understand the direction of division from the shape of "
"the symbol."

